(story)

"What the Actual Fu-." Gene says Surprised

"Meeting in my Office, Gene, Wernher and Deke. You are attending" Thomas Kerman says in Slight Anger, Trying to keep his cool.

"Acapello 11 can be Rolled out in 2 days." Wernher Explains to Thomas

"But the Astronauts will be subject to Extreme Training." Deke Adds on

Deke Kerman was a former Moho 7 Astronaut, After being diagnosed with a Heart Condition he was Put on Management Status.

"Kixon wants it Launched ASAP, Do your Job." Thomas Says Sternly

"We will try our best." Gene says in his face.

 

Reactions in the Astronaut Office wasn't The Best, Jebediah was certainly angry but he had to Hide it from the Press.

"Alright, Acapello 11, You are due to launch in 5 Days, Other News is Acapello 13 and 14 is Switching Crew, Admin wants Alan's Crew to Improve." Deke Announces

"I Expect for all of you to Keep a Level of Professionalism during This Crisis."
